com.qtplaf.library.swing

Interface EditLabel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EditField
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JCheckBoxField, JComboBoxField, JLabelField, JMaskedField, JMaskedFieldButton, JMaskedFieldDate, JPassword

    public interface EditLabel
    An edit label represents the link between the control, generally a JLabel, and the field being edited or shown.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
